Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • Brain.Command
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONParsable

    public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONParsable
    A command is a action, relative to a Domain, an Operation, and values for his parameters It contains also the sentence that has been said. One of the sentence mapped with that command in the sentence (different parameters value can occur) Finally there is an confidence value between 0-1, higher is better
